reviews.text: The chef prepares food in the open kitchen can be more hygienic.   The chef did not wear gloves to cut raw foods. Maybe it is traditional Japanese style.  However, I watched he cut fish slices and touch the trolley which collect used bowls and plates at the same time.   They should still have room to improve it.
Fairly good food at a reasonable price.
